The evidence with the title 'Ali Khamenei - Wikipedia ' says Sayyid Ali Hosseini Khamenei is a marja and the second and current supreme leader of Iran , in office since 1989. He was previously president of Iran from 1981 to 1989 . Khamenei is the second longest-serving head of state in the Middle East ( after Oman's Sultan Qaboos), as well as the second longest-serving Iranian  ... 
